unprotect-category:
Edit summary when the bot unprotects all pages from a category. Parameters:
* %(cat)s - category name
See also:
* {{msg-pywikibot|Delete-from-category}}
unprotect-images:
Edit summary when the bot unprotects all images on a page. Parameters:
* %(page)s - page title
See also:
* {{msg-pywikibot|Delete-images}}
unprotect-links:
Edit summary when the bot unprotects all pages linked from a page. Parameters:
* $(page)s - page title
See also:
* {{msg-pywikibot|Delete-linked-pages}}
unprotect-ref:
Edit summary when the bot unprotects all pages that link to/transclude a page (Special:WhatLinksHere). Parameters:
* %(page)s - page title
See also:
* {{msg-pywikibot|Delete-referring-pages}}
unprotect-simple: Edit summary when the bot unprotects a list of files.
